30662","created":1643164988,"deleted":0,"content":"村里来电话了，喜提 7 天居家隔离，emo 了","content_rendered":"<p>村里来电话了，喜提 7 天居家隔离，emo 了</p>\n","last_modified":1643164988,"replies":28,"id":830662},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/642e/92ef/48_large.png?m=1559027807","name":"tv","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/642e/92ef/48_normal.png?m=1559027807","title":"剧集","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/tv","topics":730,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"TV","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/642e/92ef/48_mini.png?m=1559027807","stars":687,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":48,"parent_node_name":"life"},"member":{"id":388030,"username":"iovekkk","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/iovekkk","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1490/878c/388030_mini.png?m=1574170695","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1490/878c/388030_normal.png?m=1574170695","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1490/878c/388030_large.png?m=1574170695","created":1551332968,"last_modified":1574170695},"last_reply_by":"avastms","last_touched":1643169155,"title":"以罗翔的视角聊一聊《开端》的结局","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/830650","created":1643163560,"deleted":0,"content":"作为罗翔老师的十年老粉，以这个视角来看《开端》的结局，实际上还是令人可惜\r\n\r\n首先王兴德夫妇，故意杀人未遂，危害社会安全(情节特别严重)，袭警（开车撞警车），数罪并罚之下，大概有生之年是出不来了，即便是出来这辈子也差不多到头了。\r\n\r\n再看那个猥琐眼镜男，猥亵罪，过失致人死亡（都不知道算不算，毕竟让王萌萌下车的是司机不是他），判个十年顶天了吧，出来以后也许还会继续为非作歹。\r\n\r\n再看结局王兴德与眼镜男的对视，本来我以为这会是王兴德的死亡凝视，接下来他一定会找机会弄死眼镜男。\r\n\r\n后来我才想起来，这是为了呼应之前的剧情：女主最终说服王兴德的话是，王兴德要活下来代替王萌萌去看到眼镜男伏法受到制裁。基于这个设定，王兴德可能就会释然，因为罪犯伏法受到制裁了。\r\n\r\n而且要给眼镜男定罪，光凭照片肯定是不行的，拍照片的那个学姐肯定还是要出庭作证的，江警官的不泄露她的身份的保证就是屁话。\r\n\r\n眼镜男坐了不到十年牢出来以后，会不会报复拍照学姐甚至是男女主，很难讲啊","content_rendered":"<p>作为罗翔老师的十年老粉，以这个视角来看《开端》的结局，实际上还是令人可惜</p>\n<p>首先王兴德夫妇，故意杀人未遂，危害社会安全(情节特别严重)，袭警（开车撞警车），数罪并罚之下，大概有生之年是出不来了，即便是出来这辈子也差不多到头了。</p>\n<p>再看那个猥琐眼镜男，猥亵罪，过失致人死亡（都不知道算不算，毕竟让王萌萌下车的是司机不是他），判个十年顶天了吧，出来以后也许还会继续为非作歹。</p>\n<p>再看结局王兴德与眼镜男的对视，本来我以为这会是王兴德的死亡凝视，接下来他一定会找机会弄死眼镜男。</p>\n<p>后来我才想起来，这是为了呼应之前的剧情：女主最终说服王兴德的话是，王兴德要活下来代替王萌萌去看到眼镜男伏法受到制裁。基于这个设定，王兴德可能就会释然，因为罪犯伏法受到制裁了。</p>\n<p>而且要给眼镜男定罪，光凭照片肯定是不行的，拍照片的那个学姐肯定还是要出庭作证的，江警官的不泄露她的身份的保证就是屁话。</p>\n<p>眼镜男坐了不到十年牢出来以后，会不会报复拍照学姐甚至是男女主，很难讲啊</p>\n","last_modified":1643164077,"replies":20,"id":830650},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1628872984","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1628872984","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":34980,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","stars":4723,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":556900,"username":"V9NN","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/V9NN","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ab5a7987d56e681a68ed920468ec7186?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ab5a7987d56e681a68ed920468ec7186?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ab5a7987d56e681a68ed920468ec7186?s=73&d=retro","created":1632620580,"last_modified":1639018103},"last_reply_by":"Innovatino","last_touched":1643167510,"title":"我如果说 Pixel 一代现在使用还很流畅，会不会被很多人打？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/830637","created":1643162302,"deleted":0,"content":"准 Pixel 一代的机子，应该是 5 、6 年前的了。\r\n\r\n原生系统，不安装任何一个国产 App ，经常使用的是 Twitter 、Chrome 、YouTube 、以及外文新闻 App 。\r\n上面安装的 app 也基本上跟着 play 更新。\r\n\r\n现在系统 Google 已经停止更新维护了，但是操作各种软件仍然很流畅。\r\n\r\n像 Twitter 、YouTube 这种大型 App ，人家也发展了这么多年，为啥它们基本都很流畅（说丝般顺滑可能被你们骂），国内的如微信、支付宝、淘宝、美团……都卡得怀疑人生？","content_rendered":"准 Pixel 一代的机子，应该是 5 、6 年前的了。<br /><br />原生系统，不安装任何一个国产 App ，经常使用的是 Twitter 、Chrome 、YouTube 、以及外文新闻 App 。<br />上面安装的 app 也基本上跟着 play 更新。<br /><br />现在系统 Google 已经停止更新维护了，但是操作各种软件仍然很流畅。<br /><br />像 Twitter 、YouTube 这种大型 App ，人家也发展了这么多年，为啥它们基本都很流畅（说丝般顺滑可能被你们骂），国内的如微信、支付宝、淘宝、美团……都卡得怀疑人生？","last_modified":1643162302,"replies":20,"id":830637},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":47246,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","stars":7681,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":410592,"username":"umumu","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/umumu","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ffa/f6b2/410592_mini.png?m=1643164748","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ffa/f6b2/410592_normal.png?m=1643164748","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ffa/f6b2/410592_large.png?m=1643164748","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ffa/f6b2/410592_xlarge.png?m=1643164748","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ffa/f6b2/410592_xlarge.png?m=1643164748","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ffa/f6b2/410592_xlarge.png?m=1643164748","created":1557376008,"last_modified":1643164748},"last_reply_by":"bthulu","last_touched":1643168183,"title":"写了个图片批量处理工具，会有人用吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/830649","created":1643163557,"deleted":0,"content":"前端渣渣，闲时无聊，写了个图片处理在线工具，目前支持：图片压缩，图片大小调整，图片裁剪，图片格式转换。后续还会加些其他功能。\r\n\r\n家人们，有什么好的建议吗？\r\n\r\nhttps://getimg.co/","content_rendered":"<p>前端渣渣，闲时无聊，写了个图片处理在线工具，目前支持：图片压缩，图片大小调整，图片裁剪，图片格式转换。后续还会加些其他功能。</p>\n<p>家人们，有什么好的建议吗？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://getimg.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://getimg.co/</a></p>\n","last_modified":1643163615,"replies":18,"id":830649},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1629391393","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":181146,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","stars":3403,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":556900,"username":"V9NN","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/V9NN","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ab5a7987d56e681a68ed920468ec7186?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ab5a7987d56e681a68ed920468ec7186?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ab5a7987d56e681a68ed920468ec7186?s=73&d=retro","created":1632620580,"last_modified":1639018103},"last_reply_by":"banricho","last_touched":1643165316,"title":"平台禁止了热更新为何很多应用仍然可以自动大变样？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/830619","created":1643155858,"deleted":0,"content":"最近发现中国联通、滴滴、支付宝都有这样的特点：\r\n没有在 AppStore 主动更新（关闭了自动更新），但是这些应用仍然自动更新了，不仅 UI 大变样，有些功能也有了变化。\r\n\r\n安卓也存在这样的情况，从 Google Play 下载的，如果应用将要内部自更新，可以从系统流量检测工具上看到大流量下载。\r\n\r\n应用内部（打开 app 后）这种强制自动更新的行为是否违规？","content_rendered":"最近发现中国联通、滴滴、支付宝都有这样的特点：<br />没有在 AppStore 主动更新（关闭了自动更新），但是这些应用仍然自动更新了，不仅 UI 大变样，有些功能也有了变化。<br /><br />安卓也存在这样的情况，从 Google Play 下载的，如果应用将要内部自更新，可以从系统流量检测工具上看到大流量下载。<br /><br />应用内部（打开 app 后）这种强制自动更新的行为是否违规？","last_modified":1643155858,"replies":17,"id":830619},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":47246,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","stars":7681,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":541279,"username":"moohng","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/moohng","website":"htttps://moohng.com","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f17366ba4e4cd03a9526f2b7a92293e?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f17366ba4e4cd03a9526f2b7a92293e?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f17366ba4e4cd03a9526f2b7a92293e?s=73&d=retro","created":1617692034,"last_modified":1643162443},"last_reply_by":"moohng","last_touched":1643167349,"title":"摸鱼摸了一个小程序","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/830653","created":1643163934,"deleted":0,"content":"花了一个星期的摸鱼时间，搞了我的第一个小程序\r\n\r\n可是身边的人都不懂，这份喜悦也不知道跟随分享，希望来这里能找一点安慰吧\r\n\r\n虽然看起来简单，不过也踩了很多坑在里面，后面有时间再整理一篇小程序`Canvas`相关的技术文章\r\n\r\n年后抽时间再加一些新的功能进去，敬请期待\r\n\r\n微信搜索** [涂图了] **即可体验\r\n\r\n现在唯一的特色功能应该就是可以将绘图的笔记保存起来，然后再自动将图模拟绘制出来。不过感觉这个功能还是有点单调，少了一些可玩性\r\n\r\n程序员的头脑只会技术😅😅😅\r\n\r\n![img]( https://moohng.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/20220125123654.jpg)","content_rendered":"<p>花了一个星期的摸鱼时间，搞了我的第一个小程序</p>\n<p>可是身边的人都不懂，这份喜悦也不知道跟随分享，希望来这里能找一点安慰吧</p>\n<p>虽然看起来简单，不过也踩了很多坑在里面，后面有时间再整理一篇小程序<code>Canvas</code>相关的技术文章</p>\n<p>年后抽时间再加一些新的功能进去，敬请期待</p>\n<p>微信搜索** [涂图了] **即可体验</p>\n<p>现在唯一的特色功能应该就是可以将绘图的笔记保存起来，然后再自动将图模拟绘制出来。不过感觉这个功能还是有点单调，少了一些可玩性</p>\n<p>程序员的头脑只会技术😅😅😅</p>\n<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://moohng.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/20220125123654.jpg\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1643163934,"replies":16,"id":830653},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_large.png?m=1595507885","name":"ideas","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_normal.png?m=1595507885","title":"奇思妙想","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas","topics":4794,"footer":"","header":"让你的创意在这里自由流动吧。","title_alternative":"Ideas","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885","stars":2519,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":519,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":548470,"username":"mcnultytrek","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mcnultytrek","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d10e/0ba6/548470_mini.png?m=1638170001","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d10e/0ba6/548470_normal.png?m=1638170001","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d10e/0ba6/548470_large.png?m=1638170001","created":1623782761,"last_modified":1638170001},"last_reply_by":"wangfeng3769","last_touched":1643170048,"title":"天下苦百度久矣，那么关于搜索引擎有什么能引入良心循环的盈利方式呢？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/830667","created":1643165815,"deleted":0,"content":"我的想法是，推出免费版本和付费版本，免费版本适合平时就用搜索引擎轻度搜索，可以理解为浅显的回答你搜索出来的问题，没有广告和诱导，能够基本解决你的问题，但是对于一些有深度的内容无法搜索出来。而付费版本则可以针对不同人群，你可以组合购买各类行业或者学科的搜索引擎，不同定位不同价格，每个人都可以根据自己的情况定制自己的搜索引擎。搜索引擎公司也可以与各大网站进行深度对接搜索，拒绝不同网站间搞对立和隔阂。","content_rendered":"<p>我的想法是，推出免费版本和付费版本，免费版本适合平时就用搜索引擎轻度搜索，可以理解为浅显的回答你搜索出来的问题，没有广告和诱导，能够基本解决你的问题，但是对于一些有深度的内容无法搜索出来。而付费版本则可以针对不同人群，你可以组合购买各类行业或者学科的搜索引擎，不同定位不同价格，每个人都可以根据自己的情况定制自己的搜索引擎。搜索引擎公司也可以与各大网站进行深度对接搜索，拒绝不同网站间搞对立和隔阂。</p>\n","last_modified":1643165815,"replies":15,"id":830667},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1629391393","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":181149,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","stars":3403,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":490275,"username":"echooo0","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/echooo0","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagl